						.ch-item.ch-img-2
							.ch-info.text-center.bg-blue-t8
								h3.text-center-imp Alex Popelard
								h4.text-center-imp Design Innovation MBA
								a.text-white-orange-hover.text-right.lsf-icon(href="http://twitter.com/alexpopelard", target="_blank" , title="twitter")
								a.text-white-orange-hover.text-right.lsf-icon(href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/alexpopelard", target="_blank" , title="linkedin")
					li
						.ch-item.ch-img-3
							.ch-info.text-center.bg-pink-t8
								h3.text-center-imp Suzee Han
								h4.text-center-imp Designer
								a.text-white-orange-hover.text-right.lsf-icon(href="http://twitter.com/suzeehan", target="_blank" , title="twitter")
								a.text-white-orange-hover.text-right.lsf-icon(href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/suzeehan", target="_blank" , title="linkedin")
					li
						.ch-item.ch-img-4
							.ch-info.text-center.bg-orange-t8
								h3.text-center-imp Michael Chen
								h4.text-center-imp Developer
								a.text-white-orange-hover.text-right.lsf-icon(href="http://twitter.com/MikeTYChen", target="_blank", title="twitter")
								a.text-white-orange-hover.text-right.lsf-icon(href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/miketychen", target="_blank" , title="linkedin")
					li
						.ch-item.ch-img-5
							.ch-info.text-center.bg-green-t8
								h3.text-center-imp Tommy Yu
								h4.text-center-imp Developer
								a.text-white-orange-hover.text-right.lsf-icon(href="https://www.facebook.com/tommy.yu.92754" , title="linkedin")
		.container-100p.bg-white
			.container-70p.margin-center.margin-bottom-5p.mobile-margin-top-150x.padding-bottom-2p
				.row
					.col-md-12.text-left.margin-top-3p
						h1.text-blue.text-big.text-normal.text-left Imagine a world with fewer, better meetings.
				.row.margin-top-1p
					.col-md-12.text-left
						h3.text-black.text-left Our team was fed up with the way meetings occupied our lives - meetings that we didn’t have to be in, meetings that ran way over time and meetings that made no decisions. After meetings, we would crawl back to our desks feeling unproductive and frustrated. 
				.row.margin-top-1p
					.col-md-12.text-left
						h3.text-black.text-left So we created SEAM, a tool to help you feel productive in the meeting room. SEAM helps you plan for focused discussions, gives you the power to move the conversation forward and aligns your team on next steps at the end of the meeting. We want to support the way you work by changing the way you meet.
				.row.margin-top-1p
					.col-md-12.text-left
						h3.text-black.text-left Meetings aren’t going to disappear forever, but better meetings lead to fewer meetings down the road. And we believe the fewer meetings the better. So give SEAM a try. And feel free to let us know what you think at contact@getseam.co. We want to make meetings better for all of us. 
				.row.margin-top-1p
					.col-md-12.text-left
						h3.text-black.text-left Ready to meet the newest member of your meetings?
				.row
					.col-md-4.col-md-offset-4.margin-top-3p
						button.btn.btn-primary.bg-pink-orange-hover.btn-lg.btn-block.border-round-5x(onClick="window.location.href='http://www.getseam.co/signUp'", role="button") GET SEAM TODAY
	div#footer-page.page.bg-drk-gray.padding-top-1p.padding-bottom-1p
		.row
			.col-md-6
				.row
					.col-md-11.col-md-offset-1.text-left.margin-top-1p
						span.text-left
							a.text-white-orange-hover.text-h2.lsf-icon(href="https://twitter.com/seam_meetings", target="_blank", title="twitter")
							a.text-white-pink-hover.text-h2.lsf-icon(href="https://www.linkedin.com/groups/Improving-Meeting-Efficiency-6671618", target="_blank", title="linkedin")
				.row
					.col-md-11.col-md-offset-1
						h4.text-left.text-white &copy; Powered by SEAM 2014.
			.col-md-6
				.row
					.col-md-offset-8.col-md-4.margin-top-1p
						img.margin-center.img-responsive.img-18p.center-box(src="../../images/logo-noWord.png" ,alt="SEAM")